      "end": 109.44000244140625,
      "text": "♪ Think it's fire when I'm sitting next to you ♪",
      "start": 104.91999816894531
    },
    {
      "end": 114.19999694824219,
      "text": "♪ Man, you're the best thing that I've had in my life, so chill out ♪",
      "start": 109.44000244140625
    },
    {
      "end": 121.5199966430664,
      "text": "♪ There's no reason to get all whispy, just be happy, hippy, hoppy, can you see that it's just me? ♪",
      "start": 115.33999633789062
    },
    {
      "end": 129.5,
      "text": "♪ Sitting here, look in my eyes, baby, you're my queen, so chill out, chill out, chill out, chill out, chill out, chill out ♪",
      "start": 121.5199966430664
    },
    {
      "end": 139.3800048828125,
      "text": "♪ There's no reason, no reason why you're all up in my face, all hysterical, wait, chill out, baby, behave ♪",
      "start": 129.5
    },
    {
      "end": 145.86000061035156,
      "text": "♪ We can be like that, I ain't going nowhere, even after this fight, I'm still here till the morning ♪",
