      "start": 145.86000061035156
    },
    {
      "end": 158.16000366210938,
      "text": "♪ My loyalty's in some ring, clean as gold, crystal clear, baby, can't you see I've been through it all? ♪",
      "start": 152.0399932861328
    },
    {
      "end": 172.0399932861328,
      "text": "♪ I want you to just understand what I'm telling you, to chill out, there's no reason for you to be all, all, all, all like, oh my god, fucking what you're saying ♪",
      "start": 158.16000366210938
    },
    {
      "end": 182.02000427246094,
